{"tid":802836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局新指引刪去部分字眼　蔡若蓮：配合課程發展需要","createTime":"2018-09-01T17:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T17:56:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49afe181e64bc3ab94b4ae07080c1e33805e0852","tid":802836,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1895000/1898695/choi_son_thumb_20170907_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1895000%2F1898695%2Fchoi_son_thumb_20170907_c_1024.jpg&h=93276ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局推出2017年版《中學教育課程指引》中文版，取代舊有課程指引。就有關國民身份認同部分，舊有指引曾提及「學校不宜強加祖國情懷於學生身上」，新指引則未有提及類似字眼。<br />\n<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮回應時表示，修訂課程指引是配合課程發展，是恆常做法。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源表示，不明白當局在新指引刪走相關字眼的用意，指本來的指引寫法合情合理，希望當局清楚交代原因。"},{"pid":"88768fa54b5568971e3e45ad89bc76210848f2c7","tid":802836,"uid":27511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"若蓮喪子"},{"pid":"199d0dcb3f4dd346a5cd90ad751e28a50cc78841","tid":802836,"uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"死得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39614a4d5fe22ee4611d5a544fecbf953d724bab","tid":802836,"uid":46500,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"死左個仔都冇吸收到教訓<br />\n<br />\n哩個世界有d人係冇得救"},{"pid":"1e14bf7d4a5033f272fe1baeca82846a631a6bbc","tid":802836,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39614a4d5fe22ee4611d5a544fecbf953d724bab","tid":802836,"uid":46500,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"死左個仔都冇吸收到教訓<br />\n<br />\n哩個世界有d人係冇得救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"可能佢個仔落到去仲要幫手教 d 港英年代嘅鬼魂要愛祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f61ed4